The Outcasts is an American teen comedy film directed by Peter Hutchings .
The film features an ensemble cast , featuring Victoria Justice , Eden Sher , Ashley Rickards , Claudia Lee , Katie Chang , Peyton List , Avan Jogia and Will Peltz .
The plot follows a group of misfit teenagers who band together to overthrow the popular clique at their high school .
Originally titled The Outskirts , filming took place between July and August 2014 .
The film was released in limited theaters and through video-on-demand on April 14 , 2017 , by Swen Releasing .